974
01:00:10,806 --> 01:00:14,142
No, you're not. Rosie, you play
Guitar Hero with the delivery guys

975
01:00:14,143 --> 01:00:15,911
while you take bets
on the phone.

976
01:00:15,912 --> 01:00:18,312
You left our
"who owes who what" cheats

977
01:00:18,313 --> 01:00:19,782
