you're a bookie.

979
01:00:21,949 --> 01:00:25,285
I do not like having these
kinds of conversations.

980
01:00:25,286 --> 01:00:27,721
And Beth,
I think you know that.

981
01:00:27,722 --> 01:00:31,459
And besides, as far as
what is legal or not legal,

982
01:00:31,460 --> 01:00:33,427
